{
  "stem": "3721.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And once in a while, they would even come in to the Schutz House-- the Swiss Schutz House.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I brought them in to this Bilitzer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we made deals, like, 10, 15 Schmeissers we bought from them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We bought from them also uniforms.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You could buy anything you wanted from the Germans.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "The only thing they wanted is, when, when it's over, you remember me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I'm the guy who helped you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And by the way, these were the same Einsatzgruppen who did all the murdering in, in, in Poland and all over.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] we were in this building.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "We rented this in Kobanya, they called it, in, in Budapest, one of the outskirts.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It was totally away from the center where the ghetto was.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And we were coming and going there, like, like, you know, like refugees from the east who ran away.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Because the Russians were already in the-- you know, like, like, four or five days after I left the city there, the Russians occupied it.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Just that close-- they, they overran.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And, and somehow, they broke through the fronts.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And they just swept Romania-- through.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And that, that came in, in a day or two.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "Like, like, when I was there, they were saying that they'll take another month or two.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "When I left, three days later, there were the Russians there already.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "So if I would have stayed, I probably would have been liberated.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But that's-- that was not my mission.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as I said, we used whatever I brought-- the funds-- to save people, mainly.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we succeeded.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Till I told you that I was in this apartment.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
